# Agent-behavior verification runtime state (spec §15 / S7-ABV) — if
# operators run the harness against the LSP-Brains Brain, the ledger
# and per-run records live under .claude/brain/ just like the other
# three Brains. Never commit.
.claude/brain/agent-behavior-feedback.jsonl
.claude/brain/agent-behavior-latest.json
.claude/brain/agent-behavior-runs/
# Judge-integrity ledger (S9-ABV-RED-3) — red-miss entries +
# triage decisions; per-deployment, never commit.
.claude/brain/judge-integrity-ledger.jsonl
# Axis 4 v1 (2026-04-22) — Skill invocation ledger fed by the
# PostToolUse hook at NeuroGrim/scripts/record-skill-invocation.sh
# when an operator runs a Claude Code session against LSP-Brains.
# Per-deployment runtime state; append-only JSONL.
.claude/brain/invocation-ledger.jsonl
